org.gvsig.tools.folders

Interface FoldersManager

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Iterable<String>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultFoldersManager

    public interface FoldersManager
extends Iterable<String>
    This class allows to keep a registry of folders associating to each folder a name, as well as to manage the location and access to the temporary files.
